1.2.1 (2013-08-27)
------------------

* Raises correct exception when calling an abstract method with arguments.

1.2.0 (2012-06-18)
------------------

* Officially supports Ruby 1.8.7, 1.9.3, REE, Rubinius (in 1.8 and 1.9 mode) and
  JRuby (in 1.8 and 1.9 mode).
* Added Travis CI integration.
* Prevented double-loading when running "bundle exec rake".
* Tweaked README.md formatting.

1.1.0 (2012-05-02)
------------------

* Tweaked README.md.

1.0.0 (2012-04-25)
------------------

* Initial release.
